OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew mum recalls horror of  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbirth at baby death unit   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A first-time mother told how she was   
OL,6, left in bloody sheets for three days at
OL,7, a maternity unit that was nearly shut  
OL,8, down in January over safety concerns.  
OL,10,FPhilippa Chapman said staff refused to 
OL,11,Fclean her bed after she had given birth
OL,12,Fat the William Harvey hospital in      
OL,13,FAshford, Kent, in March last year.     
OL,15,FShe said the birth was "horrendous",   
OL,16,Fand she would not return to the unit as
OL,17,Fshe would fear for her life.           
OL,19,FThe trust apologised to Mrs Chapman and
OL,20,Ffor its wider failings.                
